<item>
            <title>[LU-17243] Kernel 6.6 client support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17243</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Client support for 6.6 kernel.&lt;br/&gt;
-&amp;gt; flush_scheduled_work warning about flushing system_wq&lt;br/&gt;
-&amp;gt; i_ctime renamed to __i_ctime, use setters and getters.&lt;br/&gt;
-&amp;gt; mmap_write_trylock() removed, use down_write_trylock() directly.&lt;br/&gt;
-&amp;gt;nsproxy.count converted to refcount_t&lt;br/&gt;
-&amp;gt;generic_fillattr adds a mask argument.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
